{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act36side", "eventName": "泰拉飯", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DT-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "黃金蘿蔔", "storyInfo": "為了滿足工人們能在聚餐時吃到黃金蘿蔔的願望，萊歐斯小隊踏上了尋找赤金源石蟲的道路。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g4_rmbtwild_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……呼……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哼歌）", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#19$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "奇爾查克", "content": "這片荒地根本看不到頭，我們要走到什麼時候啊——"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "奇爾查克", "end": "true", "content": "喂，你這傢伙也太開心了吧……", "joined": "這片荒地根本看不到頭，我們要走到什麼時候啊——喂，你這傢伙也太開心了吧……"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哼歌）因為我得到了一件這個世界的魔法器具呀~", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過就是別人不要的東西……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，難道你看到一種全新的開鎖工具不會覺得開心嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到這個世界後，我一直覺得自己的魔法施展得沒有之前那麼順暢了，這裡好像有一股我無法利用的……奇怪的魔力。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是現在我有了這個D32鋼手電筒！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆說這種叫“D32鋼”的材料可以承載更大的能量輸出，這裡的魔法師會用它來做魔法器具，說不定我能透過它更好地使用魔法呢！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我親眼見到老闆用它施放了類似閃光魔法的法術！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#18$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫總覺得，世上不會有不需要付出努力就可以得到的好東西。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能老闆不希望好東西被白白浪費，就送給了我這個超厲害的魔法師吧~", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#16$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在對這個世界的魔法原理超感興趣的。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……那要不要趁現在多練習練習？瑪露希爾，你能試試用它把那些果子弄下來嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡長果子的樹真的很少，也就水邊有這麼幾棵，錯過了可能就沒有了。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "瑪露希爾", "content": "其實是你想吃看看那些果子吧……"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "瑪露希爾", "end": "true", "content": "好吧，就當作是練習吧，我試試好了！", "joined": "其實是你想吃看看那些果子吧……好吧，就當作是練習吧，我試試好了！"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一片安靜。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼都沒有發生呢。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼可能！之前在老闆手裡明明還能正常用的，而且我有感覺到它在回應我……！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是錯覺。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼！我試一遍！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔唔……！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是一片安靜。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是什麼都沒有發生喔。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾，這個什麼手電筒你真的能用嗎……？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然還是用法杖吧？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過是還需要適應的問題！只要給我一點時間，我就能弄懂……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿……！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#20$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicreverse"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.4, "a": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.4, "fadetime": 0.4, "a": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "ran