ure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳咳！咳咳咳咳！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……都說了不要逞強硬來啊……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事……為什麼魔法會從這個魔法器具的尾端冒出來……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們這裡的魔法器具怎麼這麼難控制……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以老夫很討厭魔法。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#15$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不一樣……！咳咳咳咳咳！！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一次，下一次我一定就能成功了！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#6$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g1_transporter", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆！這個D32鋼手電筒好像有問題——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是吧！白送給你我最寶貝的D32鋼手電筒，還要被你們找麻煩？", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……沒有！我只是想問問，你們這裡還有相關的書賣嗎？我還是想有系統地學一下……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那沒有，你以為我這裡是什麼地方？這就是一個快要倒閉的工廠，除了已經做好的武器以外就是些礦石機器，別的都沒有！", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是不想要就還給我！……我就知道，沒有一個識貨的！難道它不酷嗎？你甚至能用它照亮整片夜空！", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼好用的東西大家卻不懂得欣賞，一個都沒賣出去……害得我的工廠都要倒閉了……我本來以為終於遇到了一個有眼光的……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不是這個意思……！既然沒有就算了，等我研究明白這裡的魔法原理，我再試試看！總之……謝謝老闆的禮物！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們還是繼續去找羅德島吧——", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？又要去那片荒地嗎？這個世界太大了，光靠雙腳走，在找到羅德島之前我們就會累死吧……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……好像沒看到這裡有馬車，但是……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，你的這個……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車？", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，原來這種東西也是車……它多少錢呢？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼！雖然我的工廠要倒閉了，但這輛車還是值點錢的，你們看起來不像是能買得起的啊。", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們靠走真的能找到羅德島嗎……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，給你，午飯。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過老闆，工廠都要倒閉了，能賣點就賣點吧，要不然薪水都發不出來……", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘿蔔飯糰都吃多久了，之前你還說今天的散夥飯要請大家吃黃金蘿蔔燒烤，希望大家邁向新未來呢！", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我也要有錢請你們吃啊，把車賣了我就什麼都沒有了……！", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，幾位，我們也要開始整理做散夥飯的東西了，就不招呼你們了！", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……散夥飯？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，蘿蔔和米都在那，也沒什麼要準備的……", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們開廠第一頓飯吃的就是黃金蘿蔔呢……", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能幫你們變出來黃金蘿蔔，我早就變出來了。現在不是……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是有能力，我也想把這個儀式持續下去……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這裡吃黃金蘿蔔……是傳統嗎？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是啊。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要是聚餐，我們都會有一道黃金蘿蔔。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但今天也沒辦法了吧，現在去哪裡弄黃金蘿蔔？散夥飯嘛，有烤肉配著蘿蔔片包米飯吃，也就差不多了。", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能把你們的食材都給老夫看看嗎？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是這幾筐蘿蔔和那邊的肉……", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你要幹嘛？", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫明白了。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把食材都交給老夫吧。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫幫你們做一頓飯，讓你們能夠好好地互相告別。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊？", "name": "廠主&工人"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……？", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）先西為什麼這樣……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）你忘了，他加入我們小隊就是因為看不下去萊歐斯做飯啊。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）他大概是很難接受別人不好好吃飯吧。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃飯不僅僅是生活的一部分，其中還寄託了人們的情感……老夫都明白。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫會幫你們弄到黃金蘿蔔的。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真、真的？", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘿蔔你們這裡倒是有很多，老夫也能夠幫你們做出一頓飯來，但是黃金蘿蔔到底是什麼？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是金色的蘿蔔嗎？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幾個不是雷姆必拓人吧？", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黃金蘿蔔可是我們這裡的傳統美食。又有礦石又有蘿蔔，雷姆必拓兩大特色！", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們還吃礦石？是怎麼料理的？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃礦石？怎麼可能！黃金蘿蔔上面的金粉是“赤金源石蟲”的分泌物做的，只不過我們現在沒辦法專門花錢買這種東西了。", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過要是能找到赤金源石蟲，現做也完全沒問題。", "name": "工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫明白了。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那哪裡會有這種赤金源石蟲？", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦洞裡，荒野上，只要人少的地方都可能有。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吶，那邊的坑洞一看就是源石蟲的巢穴，那邊的礦洞口也有兩個巢穴，再那邊的洞口已經長草了，看來是被源石蟲廢棄了，應該是空的。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這附近的赤金源石蟲都被抓得差不多了，應該有點難找到呢。", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1186_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個，雖然說工廠要倒閉了，但我最後一天的工作還沒做完……要是你們能找到赤金源石蟲，我們真的會非常感謝你們的！", "name": "工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1185_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）雖然肚子確實有點餓了，但我們去羅德島的事怎麼辦？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那如果我們幫你們做出黃金蘿蔔的話，你能不能考慮便宜賣我們這輛車的事情？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我……我會考慮的。", "name": "廠主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g4_rmbtwild_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡一定有源石蟲，我都聽到牠們爬行的聲音了！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 5.0, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……這麼多！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要怎麼找到赤金源石蟲？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且源石蟲我們見過，也就大鮑勃能讓牠們安靜下來，牠們攻擊性挺強的，看起來不像是能簡單地獲得牠們分泌物的樣子啊……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來……只能戰鬥了。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都讓開，讓我再試一下這個魔法器具，這次我一定能用它正常放出魔法！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾舉起D32鋼手電筒，閉上雙眼，努力地感受蘊含在其中的能量。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她剛才可是失敗了的，現在真的可以嗎……？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下！", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——欸？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手電筒發出的光芒並沒有因為先西的打斷而停下，反而更加耀眼——"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾，不要把牠們全殺了，要殺就一隻一隻地——", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，先西……現在好像不是說這個的時候……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪露希爾拿的那個東西好像……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "