"attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要張不開眼睛了……！", "name": "萊歐斯&奇爾查克"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼回事！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊的源石蟲好像發現我們了！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了，我、我沒辦法很好地控制這個魔法器具……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，瑪露希爾，你再試一下，說不定就能成功了。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#3$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感受魔力從四周被汲取而來，力量從我的指尖流向魔法器具，然後放出——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 4.0, "ystrength": 4.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, 