 "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（謹慎地停下）", "name": "源石蟲群"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不清楚，好像我剛才釋放出了一個什麼東西，但是它消失了。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我現在又感受到它的存在了……小心！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它比我預計的還要猛烈很多！！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "…………！！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "false"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感覺到它要爆炸了！", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$runsand", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "false"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾人跑去躲在岩石後面，緊緊地縮成一團，試圖依靠岩石擋住爆炸的衝擊。"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 30.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經歷了漫長的等待之後，一絲不妙的聲響逐漸從地下傳了上來。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗞……兒……"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "isblock": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼聲音……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（謹慎地縮著）", "name": "源石蟲群"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過眼前這群看起來都不是赤金源石蟲啊……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然我們先跑，再換個地方找找看？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫剛剛覺得自己腳下似乎鬆了一下。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes"